Document: PhysicalSkyMaterial
Path: godot/classes/class_physicalskymaterial.rst
Summary: Defines a sky material for use with PhysicalSky.

Inherits: SkyMaterial < Material < Resource < RefCounted

This class is used to define a sky material for use with the PhysicalSky node. It allows for physically based sky rendering, taking into account atmospheric scattering and other physical properties to create realistic skyboxes.
